title: Alice in 9 Circles of Wonderhell
description: Alice is in Wonderhell.Transformed into a formidable warrior, Alice and her friends join a rabbit-like guide on a mission to stop the dead walking the earth. On their epic quest they meet an amazing caterpillar, the King of Hearts, an infernal Duchess, and more demonic delights as they fight through the horrific nine circles of Wonderhell.Will Alice save herself, her world and her dearest friends from the Big Boss Down Under?
author: Catt Dahman
